## Debian website copyright issues

Bdale Garbee notes that the options before us are:

* leave the site as-is
* do a lot of work and get the assignments from all contributors to relicense
  the website
* dump the website and start over, doing the licensing properly the first time

Branden Robinson notes that the latter option is already in progress, through
[wiki.debian.org](http://wiki.debian.org/).

